game.name: FZ Traffic Jam
game.description:
Traffic games have their own fan following among players from all age groups. Whether you stay at home and you have enough time to enjoy or find some free hours to have fun during a short break in your office, these games can keep you entertained amazingly. In order to give you something that is worth exploring, we have got you covered with a brand new arcade game where you have to control a car and prevent crashes. Join FZ Traffic Jam and be prepared to enjoy a fun-filled traffic adventure!

The gameplay of this cute HTML5 traffic game is very simple and easy to handle for every player. All you need to do is just by tapping on the cars you want to stop on the road. Everything looks easy to take care of initially, but challenges will keep increasing as you progress in the game. Make sure to avoid traffic jams and crashes to stay for as long as possible and create your best score. Track your present score by having a look at the top middle portion of the screen!

Try to get your car through the transport logistics and do not forget to stop vehicles, if needed! It is up to the amazing driving abilities that propel you to control the situation when the amount of cars will increase with the time. Put your insane car driving and traffic handling abilities to rule the roads and weave your vehicle through manic traffic! We are sure that our wide collection of cool HTML5 car driving games will not get you bored for a single second.
